-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduction
----
Amazon Product Finder is targeted for the home user or a seller. Program
gives its user a fast way to search the Amazon.com catalogs for various 
products and related product information. Perfect for random compulsive 
shopping experience!

Features
----
Amazon Product Finder will parse and process the XML response data and populate 
the user interface accordingly to user selected colums and detail level.

Minimum Windows System Requirements
----
Amazon Product Finder runs on Windows 2000 and Windows XP. Requires 
MSXML4.

- Microsoft Windows 2000/NT4/XP or later.
- Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 or later

